{{羅馬教廷}}
'''傳播部'''（{{lang-la|Dicasterium pro Communicatione}}<ref name="DfC">{{cite web |title=DICASTERY FOR COMMUNICATION |url=https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/segreterie/segreteria-comunicazione/documents/segreteria-per-comunicazione_profilo_en.html |publisher=The Holy See |accessdate=2020-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110132434/https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/segreterie/segreteria-comunicazione/documents/segreteria-per-comunicazione_profilo_en.html |archivedate=2020-01-10 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是[[羅馬教廷|羅馬教廷]]的一個{{link-en|羅馬教廷部會|Dicastery|部會}}。[[教宗方濟各|教宗方濟各]]於2015年6月27日以[[自動手諭|自動手諭]]型態發布的宗座信函《當前的大眾傳播》（{{lang-en|''The current context of communications''}}）成立'''傳播秘書處'''。<ref name="Vatican20150627">{{cite web |author1=Franciscus |title=FOR THE ESTABLISHMENT OF THE SECRETARIAT FOR COMMUNICATION |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/francesco/en/motu_proprio/documents/papa-francesco-motu-proprio_20150627_segreteria-comunicazione.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-07-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720175706/https://w2.vatican.va/content/francesco/en/motu_proprio/documents/papa-francesco-motu-proprio_20150627_segreteria-comunicazione.html |archivedate=2019-07-20 |language=en |date=2015-06-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>該秘書處於2018年6月23日升格，成為聖座的部會。<ref>{{cite news |title=聖座傳播秘書處升為部會 |url=https://www.vaticannews.va/zht/vatican-city/news/2018-06/pope-renames-vatican-dicastery-communication.html |accessdate=2019-07-20 |publisher=梵蒂岡新聞網 |date=2018-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720181558/https://www.vaticannews.va/zht/vatican-city/news/2018-06/pope-renames-vatican-dicastery-communication.html |archivedate=2019-07-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 簡介 ==
傳播部負責管理[[梵蒂岡城國|梵蒂岡城國]]以及[[羅馬教廷|羅馬教廷]]對外的所有大眾傳播媒介，並將羅馬教廷既有的各個出版機構及傳播媒體都納入其管轄下。包括：{{link-en|聖座新聞室|Holy See Press Office}}、梵蒂岡互聯網、[[梵蒂岡廣播電台|梵蒂岡廣播電台]]、{{link-en|梵蒂岡電視中心|Vatican Television Center}}、《[[羅馬觀察報|羅馬觀察報]]》、梵蒂岡印刷所、梵蒂岡攝影部門和{{link-en|梵蒂岡出版社|Vatican Publishing House}}。<ref name="DfC" />

設立之時，傳播秘書處的辦公室位於[[梵蒂岡電台|梵蒂岡電台]]的庇護大樓内。<ref name="Vatican20150627" />現任部長是{{link-it|保祿·魯菲尼 (記者)|Paolo Ruffini (giornalista)|保祿·魯菲尼}}，他是首位非神職人員的部長。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Pentin |first1=Edward |title=Pope Appoints Award-Winning Lay Journalist as Head of Vatican Communications |url=https://www.ncregister.com/daily-news/pope-francis-appoints-award-winning-lay-journalist-as-head-of-vatican-commu |accessdate=2019-07-20 |publisher=National Catholic Register |date=2018-07-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720182907/https://www.ncregister.com/daily-news/pope-francis-appoints-award-winning-lay-journalist-as-head-of-vatican-commu |archivedate=2019-07-20 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

